comments.text:
I really like the 4 cost changes that are different from set 13. Having one more of a key user for an item is so important to not feel stuck with a certain line.
I have great expectations for this set and I'm actually excited after watching a few videos. 
I saw animations and stuff happening and not just units auto attacking which is really cool (good job art team all spells look really cool)
I hope you guys manage to reach set 13 balance wise and thank you for listening to the community!
Can't wait!
